name: 甘奈
text:
……そっか……！
うん……甘奈……やった──……！！
trans:
...Is that so...?
Yeah, I really did it...!!

name: 甘奈
text:
甘奈、やったよ……！
プロデューサーさん……！
trans:
I was able to do it...!
Producer-san...!

name: プロデューサー
text:
確かに見てた
おめでとう……！
trans:
I watched every moment of it, Amana.
Congratulations...!

name: 甘奈
text:
……うん。甘奈、大丈夫
このまま、頑張れる──
trans:
...Yeah, I think I can manage. If I keep up this pace, I'll
need to work even harder—

name: 甘奈
text: ──絶対、決勝でも頑張ってみせるから
trans: ...I should do my very best to reach the finals.

name: 甘奈
trans:
Please guide me through this...!
Alright...!?
